title: Harry Potter and the Order of the Phoenix NTSC/U Xbox 360
description:
Harry Potter and the Order of the Phoenix:

Region      : NTSC/U                Languages: English        
Size        : 1 DVD                 Genre    : Action Adventure         
Platform    : XBOX 360              Date     : 06/2007

About:

Year Five at Hogwarts might be the most challenging yet for Harry Potter, and this game is the most immersive yet based on the mega-popular tale of the young wizard. Harry Potter and the Order of the Phoenix brings together book, film, and game like never before! You'll closely follow the book's story while exploring detailed locations at Hogwarts re-created with such detail you're almost inside the movie itself. Play as multiple characters including Harry, Sirius Black, and Dumbledore. Cast spells and wave your wand around in this magical experience so vivid you can almost feel that scar-tingle in your forehead.
